Company Summary


Vertigo Media Group Inc. was founded in 2010. The company is located in West Babylon and incorporated in New York. Vertigo Media Group Inc. specializes in Communication Services, Nec. Vertigo Media Group Inc. has 1 employees and estimated revenues of $48,000.00. 









