Vertigo Digital Displaysis now Civiq SmartscapesVertigo Digital Displays has been acquired by CIVIQ Smartscapes. Learn more
 
CIVIQ Smartscapes designs and delivers connected urban infrastructure technologies that provide access to and enhance public information, commerce, safety and efficiency to create “smartscapes” – the future of intelligent urban infrastructure. 
 
Vertigo Digital Displays will continue to operate in Canada as Civiq Smartscapes Canada Corporation.
Learn more about CIVIQ Smartscapes
 
 
 Learn More >INNOVATION ON DISPLAYIndoor and Outdoor Digital DisplaysWith more than 10,000 installed indoor and outdoor digital displays, Vertigo products offer unsurpassed performance, reliability, and aesthetic design, while maintaining the industry’s lowest Total Cost of Ownership (TCO). Vertigo has deployed digital out of home displays worldwide in locations including Toronto, New York, Chicago, London and Doha.Learn More >




































FlexVue Totem Outdoor Displays







Used in train and subway systems, bus shelters and many other out of home advertising applications, Vertigo's dynamic outdoor digital displays offer full sunlight readable technology you can depend on for any climate. Our commercial quality products are designed for 24 x 7 use and can meet the needs of any mission critical application.



















Pronto G5 Series Outdoor Displays







Our fully integrated outdoor LCD display represents the latest in sunlight readable backlight and enclosure technology. Designed for Quick Serve Restaurant (QSR) menu board applications, our patented Direct Air Cool System (DACs) offers power efficiency and reliable performance for best-in-class cost of ownership and ease of maintenance.



















Digital Out Of Home Displays







Digital out of home advertising displays offer high brightness, reliability and integrated performance in an attractive and tamper-proof enclosure. We offer a range of mall displays, elevator displays, retail solutions and more.
























































