Agency

Our PhilosophyOur philosophy is quite simple and direct.  We believe your marketing dollars are valuable and that you should receive a return on your investment. We think strategically to create results driven materials. Look – The most important thing we can do is to analyze your existing brand at its present moment and create a situation analysis. Think – Develop a brand position that is unique and true to your product; called your “Unique Selling Proposition”. This gives you the competitive edge. Create – Your brands message will be delivered consistently throughout all touch points of the sales cycle turning it into a branding and selling opportunity.
Clients[testimonials]
The Owners


Services

BrandingAt Vertigo we believe that a brand is a set of visual and verbal images that combine to convey a single mental image. The company name, logo, tagline, and campaignable image all come together to create the brand. Vertigo Media Group provides the finest Strategy, Name Development, Marketing Research, and Design Services.
BroadcastAudio and video have a unique ability to touch, engage, inspire and motivate diverse audiences. They offer businesses and organizations a powerful tool to communicate an idea, a concept, a brand by blending storytelling and emotion. Vertigo has written, art directed and produced over 18 commercials for such companies as American Express, Kraft General Foods, Kodak, Lend America, Love My Shoes, Peykar Rugs.
Direct MarketingAt Vertigo we are in the business of building business. We do it by transforming strategy, creativity and analytics into business-building ideas that have the greatest probability of selling our clients’ products to a specific audience and drive response thus creating a desired, measurable action. The communication itself may be in any of a variety of formats including Postal Mail, Direct Advertising, Direct TV, Telemarketing, E-Mail Marketing, and Point-of-Sale (POS) interactions.
AdvertisingVertigo’s approach to advertising uses a unique combination of creativity and analytics to compel interest and fascination in our clients product or service to influence the clients desired result. We put the “creativity” in Creativeness. Our writers, artists and thinkers bring emotion to the brand – and the brand closer to the consumer’s heart.
